Package: bbknnR
Title: Perform batch balanced KNN in R
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2022-05-10
Authors@R: person(given = "Yuchen", family = "Li", email = "liyuchen_1995@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: BBKNN is a fast and intuitive batch effect removal tool for single-cell data. It is originally used in the scanpy workflow, and now can be used with Seurat seamlessly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.2), Rcpp, methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp
